    <title>Projective dimension and Castelnuovo-Mumford regularity of t-spread
  ideals</title>
    <summary>  We study some algebraic invariants of $t$-spread ideals, $t\ge 1$, such as
the projective dimension and the Castelnuovo-Mumford regularity, by means of
well-known graded resolutions. We state upper bounds for these invariants and,
furthermore, we identify a special class of t-spread ideals for which such
bounds are optimal.
</summary>
